summary:
Specialties (ranked by significance)
* A/B experimentation, experiment design and analysis, hypothesis testing.
* Developer recruitment.
* On-site search, search engine infrastructure, search behaviour analysis.
* Server-side web development (Ubuntu Linux, CentOS), Object-oriented (OO) design, Perl, MySQL.
* Search engine optimization (SEO), search marketing (PPC).
* Computational biology, classification, machine learning, optimization, statistics, debugging.
* Client-side web development, Javascript, jQuery.
